            <title>[LU-16925] Lustre should build without CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16925</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the lustre build fails on kernels without CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY is set on most kernels however lustre should still build when it is not enabled.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
